co.cask.cdap.api.metrics

Class MetricDataQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.api.metrics.MetricDataQuery

  • public final class MetricDataQuery
extends Object
    Defines a query to perform on MetricStore data.

    Though limited currently in functionality, you can map MetricDataQuery to the following statement: 
     SELECT count('read.ops')                                     << metric name and aggregation function
 FROM Cube
 GROUP BY dataset,                                            << groupByTags
 WHERE namespace='ns1' AND app='myApp' AND program='myFlow'   << sliceByTags
